Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 完全遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.59,0:00:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天到最後 櫻小姐也沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻小姐到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然之前也有一直沒回來的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義之
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗議啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全校學生罷課抗議
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早天枷美夏的退學令正式發表了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事會似乎想來個速戰速決
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:03:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天校方決定對附中二年一班的天枷美夏作出退學處分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找替罪羊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教務辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要對理事會的決定提出抗議
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣播後 所有對美夏退學處分定不滿的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起擁到了教務辦公室門口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果交涉破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍對教師的行為感到不滿的學生們不願回到教室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是這麼回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉鋸戰的罷課運動於是在校內升溫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直延續到現在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我說 教導主任對學生會下達了鎮壓學生的命令哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會嗎 那音姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然當場否決
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大家都很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一班已經佔領美術室 用雕塑作路障封鎖中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打持久戰了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時可以打響第一槍哦 櫻內
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 那就好好幫他們打回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學 義之君也在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻內 你在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在主角也出現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是說曹操曹操到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你說啊 櫻內
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是大家為美夏所做的 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何一個人希望美夏離開學校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:05:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家為美夏做這麼多 我真的是非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這麼做之後會有麻煩是大家不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管大家做什麼 美夏的退學處分是不可能被取消的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是嗎 杉並
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方只是受慾望支配的醜陋的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們最多不過是給扣上不良分子的帽子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以美夏不希望為了這樣無謂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀了大家的大好前途
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼才能讓大家停下來 櫻內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把你的想法告訴大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管用什麼方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 大家一定會回應的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏的想法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈佳 廣播器材的使用方法你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？嗯 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉並 廣播室的鑰匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 我就想到會有這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試音試音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…咳…今天運勢很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 這也不用說嗎 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見學園的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家安靜地聽我說 我是二年的天枷美夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是天枷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如大家所見 現在校園內發生了大動亂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家為美夏所做的事 美夏真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很遺憾 理事會的決定 美夏已經接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個決定不能收回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓天枷退學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}天枷天枷天枷…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你去廣播室的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的事繼續下去 不但給周圍的人造成困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會給大家自身帶來麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏 美夏不希望大家為了美夏背上任何處分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏能轉入大家所在的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起享受校園生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是非常幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就剩最後三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家再讓我渡過三天充實的校園生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 美夏就可以毫無遺憾地離開風見學園了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差幾天了 就一點時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家給我一個享受平常校園生活的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 拜託了 拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一天 天枷的心意確確實實地傳到了大家的心裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀哈 杏學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 來了啊 就等你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把由夢也帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沢井
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學這麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她現在這麼開心 好像昨天什麼也沒發生一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 這樣下去真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義之也是 對天枷同學的事好像也放手不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為天枷同學希望保持那種平常的樣子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是小戀想做些什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然 因為是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但義之的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是因為討厭那樣才和義之君分手的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月島小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖沒錯 真是的 奈奈佳壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉 但如果真是這麼想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就該小戀對自己誠實一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷把自己心裡的想法告訴了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次就輪到小戀站在朋友的立場去考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼去幫助天枷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有怎麼面對義之君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來其實就是這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見了 櫻內 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利馬奧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了 義之
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 事前也沒聯繫你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是理事會臨時安排我出差
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這只是理事會為了處分天枷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使出的調虎離山之計罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像中的還輕鬆快活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已經下了決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那義之呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義之怎麼看這事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼了結了真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 說實話我也在猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想為她做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷自己並不想讓我這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她比起自己 更關心我、由夢和班長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有風見學園的所有學生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也想尊重天枷如此認真的考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓天枷就這樣繼續享受理所應當的最後一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像什麼都沒發生過一樣繼續過學校生活的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在這麼想…很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 是不是對她太冷淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是非常好的一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:14:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照義之所想的去做 這也都是為了天枷同學好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下一點時間 就一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不出什麼意外就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的願望都連成一線
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 約定好的三天期限轉眼就過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 結束了 結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊 櫻內
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎 和美夏初次相遇時的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想忘都忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拳頭我現在還痛著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別 別提那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我也覺得抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後也一直給櫻內添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 這麼鄭重地道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想道個謝的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁著風見學園的學生身份還沒失效
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心我 我不是在感傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過 要是沒有你 現在美夏還不知道怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在說些有的沒的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏也通過認識你 第一次發現人類不全是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由夢和朝倉學姐 杏學姐 花咲同學 月島
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:16:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶板橋和杉並 和大家都成了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後也和沢井解開了心結
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 櫻內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏真的是機器人與人類之間的橋樑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏的願望實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 是義之嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了這麼急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 天枷同學也在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帶上天枷同學一起來體育館
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體育館？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀這傢伙 為什麼要在體育館
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業生入場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在校生起立
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你了 天枷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個是 天枷的畢業典禮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏的畢業典禮？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 天枷同學 大家都等著你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沢井
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼時候策劃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞成這樣不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 學生會也全力協助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳乃校長也同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是多虧小戀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這三天裡月島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能讓天枷同學畢業典禮可以成功舉辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東奔西走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能為你做些什麼真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我現在可以做到的全部了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,授予畢業證書
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業證書 天枷美夏同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在任何時候都能保持健康明朗的心態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與同學相處融洽並完成了本學園所有規定課程
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特此證明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見學園校長芳乃櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}舞台的後台集合 馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台的後台？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 義之快點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士們先生們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 好戲現在才登場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 飽含爽朗和激情叫出我們對美夏的愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義之 這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 義之君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
